h3cSubnetVlan.name: h3cSubnetVlan

revisions.description: The initial revision of this MIB module.

h3cSubnetVlan.contactinfo: Platform Team Huawei 3Com Technology Co., Ltd Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R.China http://www.huawei-3com.com Zip:100085
h3cSubnetVlan.description: This MIB contains the objects for managing the subnet-based vlan configurations.

h3cSubnetNumAllVlan.name: h3cSubnetNumAllVlan
h3cSubnetNumAllVlan.description: The maximum number of subnet that can be configured on all vlans.

h3cSubnetNumPerVlan.name: h3cSubnetNumPerVlan
h3cSubnetNumPerVlan.description: The maximum number of subnet that can be configured on each vlan.

h3cSubnetNumAllPort.name: h3cSubnetNumAllPort
h3cSubnetNumAllPort.description: The maximum number of subnet that can be applied to all ports.

h3cSubnetNumPerPort.name: h3cSubnetNumPerPort
h3cSubnetNumPerPort.description: The maximum number of subnet that can be applied to each port.

h3cSubnetVlanSubnetIndex.name: h3cSubnetVlanSubnetIndex
h3cSubnetVlanSubnetIndex.description: The subnet index value of a row in this table is from zero to the value of h3cSubnetNumPerVlan subtracting one.

h3cSubnetVlanVlanIpAddressType.name: h3cSubnetVlanVlanIpAddressType
h3cSubnetVlanVlanIpAddressType.description: There are two kinds of ip address supported by vlan. One is ipv4, which is 32 bits. The other is ipv6, which is 128 bits.

h3cSubnetVlanIpAddressValue.name: h3cSubnetVlanIpAddressValue
h3cSubnetVlanIpAddressValue.description: The ip address of the configured subnet on vlan, including ipv4 and ipv6.

h3cSubnetVlanNetMaskValue.name: h3cSubnetVlanNetMaskValue
h3cSubnetVlanNetMaskValue.description: The net mask of the configured subnet on vlan, including ipv4 and ipv6.

h3cSubnetVlanRowStatus.name: h3cSubnetVlanRowStatus
h3cSubnetVlanRowStatus.description: The row status of this table.

h3cSubnetVlanPortCreateTable.name: h3cSubnetVlanPortCreateTable
h3cSubnetVlanPortCreateTable.description: Subnet-based vlan port table. Add all subnet on vlan whose vlan id is h3cSubnetVlanPortInfoVlanId into port at a draught. All of the subnet information in this port is from the h3cSubnetVlanTable above, with the value of h3cSubnetVlanPortInfoVlanId as an index, which is h3cSubnetVlanVlanId in h3cSubnetVlanTable.

h3cSubnetVlanPortCreateVlanId.name: h3cSubnetVlanPortCreateVlanId
h3cSubnetVlanPortCreateVlanId.description: The subnet-based vlan id. h3cSubnetVlanPortCreateVlanId refers to h3cSubnetVlanVlanId in h3cSubnetVlanTable. If h3cSubnetVlanPortCreateVlanId has no corresponding entry in h3cSubnetVlanTable, set operation will fail.

h3cSubnetVlanPortInfoVlanId.name: h3cSubnetVlanPortInfoVlanId
h3cSubnetVlanPortInfoVlanId.description: This vlaue is the same as the value of h3cSubnetVlanPortCreateVlanId index. All of the subnet information in this port, is described on vlan, whose vlan id is the value of h3cSubnetVlanPortInfoVlanId. The vlan id of vlan including subnet information can be gotten here. The subnet information can be gotten in the h3cSubnetVlanTable above.

h3cSubnetVlanPortRowStatus.name: h3cSubnetVlanPortRowStatus
h3cSubnetVlanPortRowStatus.description: The row status of this table.

h3cSubnetVlanCompliance.name: h3cSubnetVlanCompliance
h3cSubnetVlanCompliance.description: The compliance statement for subnet vlan MIB.

h3cSubnetVlanScalarObjectGroup.name: h3cSubnetVlanScalarObjectGroup
h3cSubnetVlanScalarObjectGroup.description: A group of scalar objects describing the maximum number.

h3cSubnetVlanSubnetGroup.name: h3cSubnetVlanSubnetGroup
h3cSubnetVlanSubnetGroup.description: A group of subnet vlan subnet.

h3cSubnetVlanPortCreateGroup.name: h3cSubnetVlanPortCreateGroup
h3cSubnetVlanPortCreateGroup.description: A group of subnet vlan port create table.
